&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a pragmatic and business-minded Sr. Legal Counsel to join our in-house legal team. In this role, you will partner with teams across the organization to provide practical legal guidance, support commercial initiatives, and help manage legal risk in a fast-moving technology environment. You’ll work on a broad range of matters including commercial contracting, intellectual property, and regulatory issues while helping the business move forward with confidence. Experience with emerging technologies, such as artificial intelligence, and a strong understanding of internet law will be considered valuable assets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&amp;nbsp;you&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
